\p
\v 18 John’s disciples and the Pharisees were fasting, and they came and asked him, “Why do John’s disciples and the disciples of the Pharisees fast, but your disciples don’t fast?” 
\p
\v 19 Jesus said to them, \wj “\+w Can\+w* \+w the\+w* groomsmen \+w fast\+w* \+w while\+w* \+w the\+w* \+w bridegroom\+w* \+w is\+w* \+w with\+w* \+w them\+w*? \+w As\+w* \+w long\+w* \+w as\+w* \+w they\+w* \+w have\+w* \+w the\+w* \+w bridegroom\+w* \+w with\+w* \+w them\+w*, \+w they\+w* \+w can\+w*’\+w t\+w* \+w fast\+w*. \wj* 
