\v 39 When he had entered in, he said to them, \wj “\+w Why\+w* \+w do\+w* \+w you\+w* \+w make\+w* \+w an\+w* \+w uproar\+w* \+w and\+w* \+w weep\+w*? \+w The\+w* \+w child\+w* \+w is\+w* \+w not\+w* dead, \+w but\+w* \+w is\+w* \+w asleep\+w*.”\wj* 
\p
